    <item>
      <title>航空公司在停运后恢复航班，旅行混乱加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/global-aviation-grinds-to-halt-as-united-delta-stop-operations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，全球范围内的航空软件故障导致航空公司缓慢恢复飞行，数千个航班延误或取消，这种混乱局面预计将持续整个周末。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/global-aviation-grinds-to-halt-as-united-delta-stop-operations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 08:22:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>从 ATM 到航班，史诗级 IT 崩溃留下一片混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/microsoft-cloud-service-issues-disrupt-air-travel-operations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，网络安全公司 CrowdStrike Holdings Inc. 的一次失败的软件更新导致全球无数 Microsoft Windows 计算机系统崩溃，这将成为全球有史以来最严重的 IT 故障。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/microsoft-cloud-service-issues-disrupt-air-travel-operations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 03:31:32 GMT</pubDate>
